{"tid":2383400,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚]股票市場之烏托邦論","createTime":"2021-01-28T01:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:09:29.000Z","uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa838a15d876d069805ba001e73f686c200c950","tid":2383400,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"拋磚<br />\n現世代能否共同建構一個市場型態<br />\n使股票之買賣不再是零和遊戲？<br />\n一方的盈利不一定意味另一方的損失<br />\n致使市場無一人輸而全部也有盈利？<br />\n烏托邦式股市系統是否可行？<br />\n例如設定所有股票只能上升<br />\n或是市場懲罰所有沽空者<br />\n原則類似於永動機的探究<br />\n一方面股票市場繼續日常運行<br />\n另一方面人人皆可從中獲利<br />\n而並沒有損失的風險<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db14c1a47bd49b0436e84960a3009bdb9e3d7e83","tid":2383400,"uid":69159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"23歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bb152be7b211f9394fd5e1b7a3816ac671f893","tid":2383400,"uid":642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:21:21.000Z","msg":"有人賣就有人輸"},{"pid":"4c193136585046affdf79c7392c7ba74392966eb","tid":2383400,"uid":120264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"咁咪無人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791d81d783955419b33f60a292c170182ffa2168","tid":2383400,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"冇博奕既市場唔係自由經濟<br />\n<br />\n正和產品請去債券市場"},{"pid":"66b8e59ab221258291795f1488d63107f8e7891c","tid":2383400,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db14c1a47bd49b0436e84960a3009bdb9e3d7e83","tid":2383400,"uid":69159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"23歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"接近看破紅塵的感覺"},{"pid":"77ae4c5cb1567ad841992a1677883d0bf9769897","tid":2383400,"uid":24641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d77c6f533598f54d72acbbc27253ab34eff70d","tid":2383400,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c193136585046affdf79c7392c7ba74392966eb","tid":2383400,"uid":120264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"咁咪無人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"上世紀初經濟大蕭條<br />\n曾經一度興起共產主義與資本主義的兩種烏托邦論<br />\n然而資本主義烏托邦沒有解決財富不均現象<br />\n而共產主義烏托邦沒有提供社會進步的誘因<br />\n本人提出的新烏托邦論<br />\n希望是接近溶合二者之優勝之處<br />\n但暫時未有想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9b214a8b3a37e245d484670980bfaae1c8c3bd","tid":2383400,"uid":39812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"股票市場唔係零和遊戲<br />\n衍生品市場先係零和遊戲"},{"pid":"adde8da3e3a006ab85614827b75489086e8b6b6c","tid":2383400,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ae4c5cb1567ad841992a1677883d0bf9769897","tid":2383400,"uid":24641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"所以樓主表示暫時沒有實際想法<br />\n但最大的缺陷誠如巴打所言<br />\n就如永動機至今仍未面世"},{"pid":"adb1b66904dd06976788d8f472fb12ae5039bef9","tid":2383400,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f9b214a8b3a37e245d484670980bfaae1c8c3bd","tid":2383400,"uid":39812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"股票市場唔係零和遊戲<br />\n衍生品市場先係零和遊戲"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"股票市場不是零和遊戲？<br />\n可否更詳述之？<br />\n本人以為一人的盈利必然來自一人的損失<br />\n在封閉的股票市場<br />\n不會有更多的資產增加<br />\n則總資產守恆"},{"pid":"ba4d72fb46dd4f63e1ddb78de4f026c00f2baf8a","tid":2383400,"uid":2